# My API

Defines attributes for both request and response using different available options.

# Create user [POST /user]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + name: John (string, required) - User name
        + email: `admin@localhost` (string, optional)
        + age: 42 (number)
        + comment

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + status: `ok` (required, fixed)
